leadingComments.value:
Automated checks to catch errors before publishing a news update: - The element's datetime attribute is set to the date of the update. - The element's text content is set to the date of the update. - The id of the
is unique and follows the format 'news-YYYY-some-topic'. - All elements have a target="_blank" attribute. - All elements have an href attribute. - All elements have alt and non-empty src attributes. - Grave accent characters are checked for, as they should likely be elements. HTML validity checking is not performed.
